msgctxt "an6.5:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Āhuneyyavagga "
msgstr "1. Worthy of Offerings "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Paṭhamaājānīyasutta "
msgstr "5. The Thoroughbred (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an6.5:1.1"
msgid "“Chahi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro assājānīyo rājāraho hoti rājabhoggo, rañño aṅgantveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a fine royal thoroughbred with six factors is worthy of a king, fit to serve a king, and is considered a factor of kingship. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an6.5:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.5:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, rañño bhadro assājānīyo khamo hoti rūpānaṃ, khamo saddānaṃ, khamo gandhānaṃ, khamo rasānaṃ, khamo phoṭṭhabbānaṃ, vaṇṇasampanno ca hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a fine royal thoroughbred can endure sights, sounds, smells, tastes, and touches. And it’s beautiful. "

msgctxt "an6.5:2.3"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro assājānīyo rājāraho hoti rājabhoggo, rañño aṅgantveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "A fine royal thoroughbred with these six factors is worthy of a king, fit to serve a king, and is considered a factor of kingship. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.283, sc3
msgctxt "an6.5:3.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant with six factors is worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is the supreme field of merit for the world. "

msgctxt "an6.5:3.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.5:3.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti rūpānaṃ, khamo saddānaṃ, khamo gandhānaṃ, khamo rasānaṃ, khamo phoṭṭhabbānaṃ, khamo dhammānaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant can endure sights, sounds, smells, tastes, touches, and thoughts. "

msgctxt "an6.5:3.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these six factors is worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is the supreme field of merit for the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.5:3.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

